---
import Card from "../../unitComponents/Card.astro";
import LearnBtn from "../../unitComponents/LearnBtn.astro";
import Planos from "../../../assets/images/planos.webp";
import IAD1 from "../../../assets/images/About/Improvement/IAD1.jpg";
import IAD2 from "../../../assets/images/About/Improvement/IAD2.jpg";
import IAD3 from "../../../assets/images/About/Improvement/IAD3.jpg";
import IAD4 from "../../../assets/images/About/Improvement/IAD4.jpg";
---

<section class="w-full">
    <div class="w-full flex justify-center">
        <img src={Planos.src} alt="">
    </div>
    <div class="w-full px-8 md:px-52 font-bold my-10">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl text-grisT">
            IMPROVEMENT IN SYSTEMS AND DESIGNS
        </h1>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full px-8 md:px-52 font-bold">
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-grisT">
            All our systems are engineered to meet the highest international standards and are carefully tailored
             to comply with the specific regulations of the country or state where the equipment will be installed.
        </p><br>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-grisT">
            Our top-tier engineering and design team is composed of specialized, experienced engineers who utilize advanced
             tools and simulation software to develop new industrial systems and optimize existing ones.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full px-8 md:px-52 font-bold my-16">
        <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-redBg text-center">
            A reliable and productive equipment starts with a perfect and <br>detailed design
        </h2><br>
        <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl text-black text-center">
            Our design approach directly addresses common issues and inefficiencies found in other brands.
        </h3>
    </div>
    <div>
        <img src="" alt="">
    </div>
    <div class="w-full px-8 md:px-80 font-bold">
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-grisT text-center">
            Using finite element analysis software (AnsysÂ®), we conduct precise tests to evaluate the behavior of
             new designs, improvements to current designs, and custom orders through computer simulations.
              This rigorous testing ensures the quality and reliability of our products.
        </p><br>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6 text-base md:text-lg text-grisT">
            <li>Behavior of the flow of aggregates and air at any point in the process.</li>
            <li>Analysis of temperatures, their use and their isolation.</li>
            <li>Analysis of structural, static and dynamic efforts, during the operation and 
                in the installation and dismantling maneuvers.
            </li>
            <li>
                Analysis of the behavior of air and dust flow in cyclone separators and baghouses for pollution control.
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full grid grid-cols-4 gap-10 px-8 font-bold text-black text-base md:text-lg my-16">
        <Card>
            <h3 class="text-center">Dust flow in a baghouse</h3>
            <div class="w-full">
                <img src={IAD1.src} alt="" class="min-w-full min-h-[250px]">
            </div>
        </Card>
        <Card>
            <h3 class="text-center">Dust flow in a baghouse</h3>
            <div class="w-full">
                <img src={IAD2.src} alt="" class="min-w-full min-h-[250px]">
            </div>
        </Card>
        <Card>
            <h3 class="text-center">Dust flow in a baghouse</h3>
            <div class="w-full">
                <img src={IAD3.src} alt="" class="min-w-full min-h-[250px]">
            </div>
        </Card>
        <Card>
            <h3 class="text-center">Dust flow in a baghouse</h3>
            <div class="w-full">
                <img src={IAD4.src} alt="" class="min-w-full max-h-[250px]">
            </div>
        </Card>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full px-8 md:px-64 font-bold flex flex-col gap-10">
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-grisT text-center">
            ...and After the design and manufacturing process, we continue to monitor equipment performance through
             the maintenance services we provide. This ongoing feedback allows us to continuously improve future production,
              resulting in some of the most reliable and productive equipment on the market.
        </p>
        <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-grisT text-center">Custom Design</h1>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-grisT text-center">
            In addition to our standardized designs, we specialize in customized solutions tailored to the specific needs
             of each client. Whether adapting to unique environmental conditions or meeting precise performance requirements,
              our team works closely with customers to develop systems that deliver unmatched reliability and efficiency.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full grid grid-cols-4 gap-10 px-8 font-bold text-black text-base md:text-lg my-16">
